16-Hole Titanium Nail Head for 16mm Coil

Our Made in the USA Titanium is a must try experience!

[click to view our shipping policies]

Description for Part Number 2101 

  • Fits all the dabbing specialists Nail Bodies, P/N 3101, 3102, 3201, and all nail bodies with 5/16-18" threaded connection
  • Material: Grade 2 Titanium 99.4% Pure, Melted in the USA
  • Engineered, Designed, & CNC Machined in the USA
  • Deburred and Sterilized Using a Special Process

This is the Finest Titanium Nail Made:

  • The Bowl is Designed to not “Never Lose a Dab”, with no holes in the bottom
  • The 16 Holes Drilled at an Angle, All Meet Together in the Single Hole on the Opposite Side, Causing a “Vortex Effect” and Super Positive Airflow
  • Dabs Taste Better and Last Longer
  • Q-tip swab after each use to maintain high-quality taste
  • Soak in hot alcohol for a thorough cleaning and use small scraper and Q-tip, rinse with hot water. 
  • Use with P/N 5101 the dabbing specialists Custom Enail Made in the USA, or any enail with 16mm heater coil.

*Engineered to use at a coil temperature setting of 800 degrees Fahrenheit.
